Netizen contribution
The incident attracted a large number of people from the surrounding area to watch. According to netizens, the power supply to Yangbadao Village where the incident occurred has been cut off, all non-official vehicles have been asked to turn around, and all live broadcasts will be cut off within a few minutes.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: An earlier video showed a group of uniformed personnel spraying pepper spray on people along the street, while another group of people followed closely behind and recorded and live-streamed the incident.
